@rootUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1/employees

### 1. Contratar un nuevo empleado
POST {{rootUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cui": "1234567890123",
  "nit": "123456789",
  "fullname": "Juan Pérez López",
  "email": "juan.perez@hospital.com",
  "phoneNumber": "12345678",
  "birthDate": "1985-05-15",
  "departmentCode": "MED-025",
  "startDate": "2024-01-15",
  "salary": 15000.00,
  "igssPercent": 0.04,
  "irtraPercent": 0.01,
  "notes": "Contratación inicial como médico general"
}

### 2. Contratar otro empleado para pruebas
POST {{rootUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cui": "9876543210987",
  "nit": "987654321",
  "fullname": "María García Hernández",
  "email": "maria.garcia@hospital.com",
  "phoneNumber": "87654321",
  "birthDate": "1990-08-22",
  "departmentCode": "ENF-025",
  "startDate": "2024-01-20",
  "salary": 8000.00,
  "igssPercent": 0.04,
  "irtraPercent": 0.01,
  "notes": "Enfermera jefe"
}

### 3. Obtener todos los empleados
GET {{rootUrl}}

### 4. Obtener empleados con filtros
GET {{rootUrl}}?q=Juan&department=MED-025&isActive=true

### 5. Obtener empleado por CUI
GET {{rootUrl}}/1234567890123

### 6. Promover empleado a gerente de departamento
POST {{rootUrl}}/1234567890123/promote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "salaryIncrease": 5000.00,
  "departmentCode": "ADM-025",
  "date": "2024-06-01",
  "notes": "Ascenso a jefe de departamento de Medicina General"
}

### 7. Aumento de salario
POST {{rootUrl}}/9876543210987/salary-increase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "salaryIncrease": 2000.00,
  "date": "2024-06-15",
  "notes": "Aumento por desempeño excepcional"
}

### 8. Terminar contrato de empleado
DELETE {{rootUrl}}/9876543210987
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2024-11-01",
  "terminationType": "RENUNCIA",
  "reason": "Renuncia voluntaria"
}

### 9. Recontratar empleado
POST {{rootUrl}}/9876543210987/rehire
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "99998888",
  "departmentCode": "ADM-025",
  "newSalary": 5000.00,
  "igssPercent": 0.04,
  "irtraPercent": 0.01,
  "startDate": "2025-01-01",
  "notes": "Recontratación en administración"
}

### 10. Intentar promover a un empleado que ya es gerente (debería fallar)
POST {{rootUrl}}/9876543210987/promote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "salaryIncrease": 3000.00,
  "departmentCode": "ADM-025",
  "date": "2025-01-02",
  "notes": "Segundo ascenso - debería fallar por gerente duplicado"
}

### 10. Intentar promover a un empleado que ya es gerente (debería fallar)
